These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop, house, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | punk | hip-hop   | ambient | house    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: hamburg, nizza, miami, paris
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | paris    | hamburg | miami | nizza    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, collecting, gardening, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Hobby          | camping | gardening | collecting    | singing      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
City: paris, colone, nizza, san-francisco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person traveling to colone is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| City         | san-francisco | paris | colone | nizza |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, bird, fish
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the owner of the fish##1
3. the indian is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | pony  | hedgehog    | bird   | fish       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, tower, colonial
1. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the tower house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| House   | colonial | ranch-style     | cape-cod  | tower  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, house, metal, punk
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the person driving the ship is the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | punk | metal | house    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

