.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, project-manager, teacher
House: futuristic, palace, ranch-style, tower
1. the tower house is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the coach is between the teacher and the pilot##2
6. the palace house is in an odd position##4
7. the palace house is between the coach and the ranch-style house##2
8. the coach is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| House   | futuristic  | tower | palace    | ranch-style            |

