.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, bridge, domino
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing poker and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Game    | domino     | poker | backgammon     | bridge  |

