.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game, baccarat, prince
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the prince-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the prince-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Cigar   | baccarat | game | prince        | bongani    |

