.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian, turkish, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, argentine-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the canadian##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is argentine-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is argentine-polo is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the nigerian is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | canadian   | argentine   | nigerian      | turkish      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | argentine-polo | biathlon |

