.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
City: miami, hamburg, edinburgh, hannover
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
5. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| City   | hamburg | miami | edinburgh    | hannover |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

