.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: snooker, domino, bridge, mah-jongg
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person playing bridge##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | bridge | snooker | domino    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

