.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, monopoly, chess
There 4 different types of food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
3. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
7. the person eating corn is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Game   | chess | canasta    | monopoly       | backgammon |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

