.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, kale, cucumber, papaya
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person eating kale is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Food     | nectarine      | cucumber       | kale | papaya     |

