.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, vegafina, tiparillo
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
3. the baccarat-smoker is between the entrepreneur and the oliveros-smoker##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Cigar   | tiparillo          | baccarat | oliveros         | vegafina  |

 